yAppliesToRange</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C6:C10&quot;</span>))\n    top.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Rank</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
